<text top="661" left="90" width="69" height="18" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="703" left="122" width="395" height="13" font="1">The situation concerning the Democratic Republic of the Congo</text>
<text top="739" left="153" width="675" height="13" font="1">Second report of the Secretary-General on the United Nations Preliminary Deployment in the Democratic</text>
<text top="757" left="153" width="302" height="13" font="1">Republic of the Congo (S/1999/1116 and Corr.1)</text>
